parameters:
Zerachiel: I have a bad feeling... It
might be better to prepare properly.

Zerachiel: Before moving forward, let's
ask Unie and Ishvald about the
situation.

Uniye: Several angels are aiming for the
antidote, so Mel-sama took her friends
and escaped deeper inside!!

Uniye: I don't know for sure! But it's
true that Mel-sama is being chased!!
Zerachiel: Alright, leave it to us.

Uniye: Thank you very much...! Please,
I'm counting on you!!

Uniye: I will defend this place no
matter what!!
Unié: Please take care of Mel-sama...!!

Zerachiel: I'll leave this place to you,
Unié.

Knight: Haa haa... I'm fine... But more
importantly, Mel-sama...

Knight: Haa haa... There are too many
angels...

Knight: If the Demon Lord-sama were
here, these guys...

Maid: You want to go further inside,
right?

Maid: May the blessings of Henri be upon
you...

Maid: Some angels headed towards the
back...

Ishvald: Zerachiel, I'm glad you're
safe.

Ishvald: We're fine. However, many of
our brethren have been taken down...
Ishvald: Leave this to us, go ahead.

Zerachiel: Thank you, I'll leave it to
you.
